# RepoLedger

Repository Ownership History & Access Control System.

## Owner
- **Name:** Danial Zivehdar
- **Email:** danialzivehdar1992@gmail.com

## Features
- Linear ownership history tracking
- Secure direct link (owner-only access)
- Token-based authentication
- Auto-expiry (24 hours)

## Usage
```bash
javac RepoOwnerAccess.java
java RepoOwnerAccess
